Class Hour

java.lang.Object
com.example.lab_3javafx.J2_Lab3_Karpenko.taskone.Hour
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Hour>
public class Hour extends Object implements Comparable<Hour>
The Hour class represents an hour with a number of passengers and a comment. It implements the Comparable interface to allow for sorting by the number of passengers.
